'''DWLC''' (1017 kHz [[Lucena, Philippines|Lucena]]) is an [[AM broadcasting|AM]] [[radio station]] owned and operated by [[Philippine Broadcasting Service]] in the [[Philippines]]. Its studios and transmitters are located at [[Lucena City]], [[Quezon Province|Quezon]].
